### * CASSAVA API TESTS ###

@port = 8080
@baseUrl = http://localhost:{{port}}/api

### * Add Cassava Detection Record
POST {{baseUrl}}/cassava
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "detectedType": "Healthy",
  "actualType": "Diseased",
  "image": "http://example.com/uploads/cassava-leaf.jpg",
  "user": "68c0b3d5de96e64d24ef7c24"
}

### * DETECTION
GET {{baseUrl}}/detect

### * Get All Cassava Records (with filters & pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cassava?page=1&limit=10&detectedType=Diseased&actualType=Diseased

### * Get All Cassava Records (with filters & pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cassava?page=1&limit=10&user=68df139c55fec5c5fe0a473c&createdAt=2025-10-07

### * Get One Cassava Record
GET {{baseUrl}}/cassava/68c0b3f9de96e64d24ef7c26

### * Update Cassava Record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cassava/68c0b3f9de96e64d24ef7c26
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "detectedType": "Diseased",
  "actualType": "Diseased",
  "image": "http://example.com/uploads/cassava-leaf-updated.jpg"
}

### * Delete Cassava Record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cassava/68c0bae59caa63dbb4bd6055